{"id":36394,"date":"2021-05-30T11:10:02","date_gmt":"2021-05-30T07:10:02","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/?p=36394"},"modified":"2023-08-31T21:10:18","modified_gmt":"2023-08-31T17:10:18","slug":"salat-al-duha-fi-masjid","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/05\/30\/salat-al-duha-fi-masjid\/","title":{"rendered":"Hadith on Duha: Forenoon prayer is better than spoils"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, dispatched a company that acquired a great amount of spoils and returned quickly. A man said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, we have not had a company of our people return more quickly with greater spoils!\u201d The Prophet said, \u201c<strong>Shall I not tell you of a swifter return and greater spoils than this company? A man who performs ablution in the best manner, then sets out to the mosque to pray in it in the morning and ends with forenoon prayer. He has a swifter return and greater spoils.<\/strong>\u201d<\/p>\n<p>Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Ibn H\u0323ibba\u0304n 2535<\/p>\n<p>Grade: <em>Jayyid<\/em> (very good) according to Al-Albani<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\">\u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0647\u064f\u0631\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0628\u064e\u0639\u064e\u062b\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0645\u064e \u0628\u064e\u0639\u0652\u062b\u064b\u0627 \u0641\u064e\u0623\u064e\u0639\u0652\u0638\u064e\u0645\u064f\u0648\u0627 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u063a\u064e\u0646\u0650\u064a\u0645\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0648\u064e\u0623\u064e\u0633\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0639\u064f\u0648\u0627 \u0627\u06